title: David Leadbetter - Golf - The Short Game
description:
David Leadbetter, world renown golf teacher, demonstrates in this video
which shots to play in different situations and how to develop the touch
necessary for a great short game.  This video is divided into four segments:
putting, chipping, pitching and bunker play.
The short games accounts for 60 per cent or more of your golf score. We can
improve our scores dramatically by practicing the short game. This video will
give you the tools to score better.  Have a good golf day and enjoy.
